The '''thought-caste''' were a caste of [[Sumria]]s from the [[Lol system/Legends|Lol system]]. They had four digits on each hand, which was the probable reason for the development of base-eight mathematics by the Sumrian people. This base-eight mathematics resulted in the development of the [[Df]] scale, a measurement of the effective range of [[Artillery/Legends|artillery]].

